Package com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.graphs.dag

Class Edge<V,E>

java.lang.Object
com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.graphs.dag.Edge<V,E>
Type Parameters:
V - the type of the vertices of the edge
E - the type of the attribute associated with the edge
public class Edge<V,E> extends Object
The Edge class represents a directed edge in a graph between two vertices, with an optional attribute.
